  <div style="padding: 25px;"></div>
  <div class="info">
    Soccer Duel, a 1v1 soccer game created by Felix Figueroa. Heavy players tend
    to win the ball in duels, and they have the best shooting stats. Light players
    are crazy fast, but they are weak and have poor shooting. Normal players are
    average, running and shooting well, but they have no special advantage. 
    Ensure that python 3 is installed on your device.
  </div>
  <div class="info"> 
    <u>Option 1:</u><br>
    Unzip soccergame.zip and then open README.txt. Follow the instructions to play. The device must use bash.
  </div>
  <div class="info"> 
    <u>Option 2:</u><br>
    Unzip soccergame.zip. You can now run game.py anyway you wish.
  </div>

