    Graphical Adventure is a visual text-based exploration game by Judah Johnson. Players navigate a strange environment using on-screen prompts and logic-based choices. The game blends storytelling and interactive puzzles with basic Python graphics. 
    Ensure that Python 3 is installed on your device.
  </div>
  <div class="info">
    <u>Option 1:</u><br>
    Download and unzip the folder. Open <code>README.txt</code> if available, and follow the instructions. Use a terminal with bash.
  </div>
  <div class="info">
    <u>Option 2:</u><br>
    Open a terminal in the unzipped folder and run <code>python3 game.py</code>.
